      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个智能体工作流的流程图。整体思路是：从start节点出发，先到agent，然后agent可以触发action，最后都汇聚到end。你看这个结构能表达吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "__start__",
        "agent",
        "action",
        "__end__"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，我理解为四个核心节点：起点、agent智能体、action动作、终点。连接关系上，start到agent是实线，agent到action也是实线对吧？那action和end之间呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "__start__",
        "agent",
        "action",
        "__end__"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "action和end之间不用直接连，让agent连到end就行。另外agent和action之间我想用虚线表示，表示这是一种可选的触发关系，不是必然的流程走向。start和agent之间保持实线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "agent",
        "action",
        "__end__"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我画了一下：start用圆角矩形，agent和action用普通矩形，end也用圆角矩形。连接关系是start→agent实线，agent→action虚线，agent→end虚线。这样对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "__start__",
        "agent",
        "action",
        "__end__"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "连接关系对的，但我注意到end节点的样式，希望它和start有所区分。start作为入口可以做得低调一点，end作为终点要突出显示，比如用紫色填充。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "__start__",
        "__end__"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "收到，我把start做成透明填充，end用紫色#bfb6fc。另外我统一设置了默认节点的背景色为淡紫色#f2f0ff，行高1.2，这样整体风格一致。您看看效果？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "__start__",
        "__end__",
        "classDef default",
        "classDef first",
        "classDef last"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "整体不错，但有个细节：action到agent的箭头方向反了。应该是agent指向action，表示agent触发action，而不是action指向agent。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "agent",
        "action"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，现在agent→action是虚线箭头，方向正确了。我检查了一遍所有连接：start→agent实线，agent→action虚线，agent→end虚线。还有需要调整的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "agent",
        "action",
        "__start__",
        "__end__"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题了，这个流程图准确表达了智能体的工作机制：从start进入，由agent决策，可选择性触发action，最终到达end。样式区分也很清晰，可以定稿了。",
